OL,3,CWorkplace parking charge proposed by
OL,4,CCardiff Council for local businesses
OL,6,FA new Workplace Parking charge has
OL,7,Fbeen favoured by Cardiff Council's
OL,8,FCabinet rather than imposing a
OL,9,Fcongestion charge for drivers in the
OL,10,Fcity.
OL,12,FThe new parking levy could be imposed
OL,13,Fon certain businesses with parking
OL,14,Fspaces on their premises.
OL,16,FThe Council says it would use the
OL,17,Fmoney raised from the parking levy to
OL,18,Fimprove public transport in Cardiff.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
