OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1784290699
OL,3,CWorkplace parking charge proposed by
OL,4,CCardiff Council for local businesses
OL,6,FIt is expected that the council will
OL,7,Fplace an annual charge on the spaces
OL,8,Flocated within the local authority
OL,9,Farea.
OL,11,FInspiration for the charge has been
OL,12,Ftaken from cities, like Nottingham,
OL,13,Fwhich have already implemented a
OL,14,Fsimilar and successful scheme.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1784290699
OL,3,CWorkplace parking charge proposed by
OL,4,CCardiff Council for local businesses
OL,6,FWhile there is not much detail on how
OL,7,FCouncil would carry this out, if they
OL,8,Fwere to follow the Nottingham model
OL,9,Fthe charges would apply to larger
OL,10,Fbusinesses with 11 or more spaces,
OL,11,Fwhilst smaller businesses and
OL,12,Fhospitals would be exempt.
OL,14,FGareth Hillman is the managing
OL,15,Fdirector at a local scaffolding
OL,16,Fcompany which is against the proposed
OL,17,Fmovement and feels that it would be
OL,18,F"just another tax" on his business.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
