FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1784290699
OL,3,CWorkplace parking charge proposed by
OL,4,CCardiff Council for local businesses
OL,6,FHe believes in the construction sector
OL,7,Fit would be impossible to navigate and
OL,8,Fhe tells us he cannot expect his staff
OL,9,Fto travel on public transport.
OL,11,FCllr Dan De'Ath, the Cabinet Member
OL,12,Ffor Climate Change, Strategic Planning
OL,13,Fand Transport says that Cardiff has
OL,14,Fone of the highest numbers of car
OL,15,Fowners, which is "putting increasing
OL,16,Fpressure on our road network".
OL,18,FHe adds that more people travelling
OL,19,Fvia public transport would be better
OL,20,Ffor businesses.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
