FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1784290699
OL,3,CWorkplace parking charge proposed by
OL,4,CCardiff Council for local businesses
OL,6,FProfessor of Logistics and Transport
OL,7,Fat Cardiff University, Andrew Potter,
OL,8,Fsays many motorists will not be
OL,9,Fimpacted by the proposed levy.
OL,11,FHe continues "it is less of a charge
OL,12,Fon the driver, and more of a charge on
OL,13,Fthe space the cars will use when they
OL,14,Fare parked up" and that it is far
OL,15,Fcheaper scheme to implement than a
OL,16,Fcongestion charge.
OL,18,FITV Cymru Wales contacted the Welsh
OL,19,FGovernment for a statement, to which
OL,20,Fthey responded: "This is a matter for
OL,21,FCardiff Council".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/5
